<td colspan=2 valign=top>An inline attachement is a file, witch can be placed in the "normale" text-flow. Inline attachments <b>will only be stored 3 months</b> past the last display! After this time, these attachments will be automaticly deleted. If the attachement is deleted, there is no way to recover it.<br><br>
Actualy there are only attachment of type JPG allowed. Please don't attach any security related files! Inline attachments haven't any special access control.
